\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104anh1665702601480.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/anh1665702601480.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/anh1665702601480.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"anh1665702601480\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n $formdb (deprecated)\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"anh1665702601480___formdbdeprecated__266669\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return a value that indicates whether data in the current Form has been retrieved from a database.\n </p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"anh1665702601480__note_w155ab1b7b3_w156ab1b7_w157ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formdb</span> function is deprecated. It has been\n         superseded by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancedb</span>, which is applicable to all component types.\n         For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dmr1665702598068.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dmr1665702598068.html\" title=\"Return an indication whether data in the current instance has been retrieved from a database.\">$instancedb</a>. </div>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"anh1665702601480__topic_d83864e1_d83865e1_d83866e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"anh1665702601480__p_d83867e1_d83868e1_d83869e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Return</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formdb</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"anh1665702601480__topic_d55462e1_d55463e1_d55464e1_d55465e1_d55466e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1198981e88\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"anh1665702601480__table_d8672e1_d8673e1_d8674e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formdb</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"anh1665702601480__table_d8672e1_d8673e1_d8674e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"anh1665702601480__table_d8672e1_d8673e1_d8674e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"anh1665702601480__table_d8672e1_d8673e1_d8674e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"anh1665702601480__table_d8672e1_d8673e1_d8674e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">In the following cases:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"anh1665702601480__li_d34355e1_d34356e1_d34357e1\">No entities have been retrieved\n                              from a database. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"anh1665702601480__li_d34358e1_d34359e1_d34360e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formdb</span> has\n                              been reset to 0 by a ProcScript statement. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"anh1665702601480__li_d34361e1_d34362e1_d34363e1\">No entities are painted on the\n                              form. </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"anh1665702601480__table_d8672e1_d8673e1_d8674e1__entry__1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"anh1665702601480__table_d8672e1_d8673e1_d8674e1__entry__2\">An entity in the form has been retrieved from a\n                        database. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"anh1665702601480__topic_d55467e1_d55468e1_d55469e1_d55470e1_d55471e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1198981e160\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"anh1665702601480__d5909e20\">Use in Form components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"anh1665702601480__topic_d55472e1_d55473e1_d55474e1_d55475e1_d55476e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1198981e170\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"anh1665702601480__p_d83882e1_d83883e1_d83884e1\">Use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formdb</span> to test whether any occurrence in the Form has been retrieved from a database. The value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formdb</span> is actually the inclusive logical OR of all the entity-level flags indicating database origin.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"anh1665702601480__p_d83885e1_d83886e1_d83887e1\">Statements that affect the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formdb</span> are the same as those that affect <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancedb</span>, and the return values are determined in the same way.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525786\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525786\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$formdb (deprecated) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $formdb (deprecated) Return a value that indicates whether data in the current Form has been retrieved from a database. Note: The $formdb function is deprecated. It has been superseded by $instancedb , which is applicable to all component types. For more information, see $instancedb . Return = $formdb Return Values Table 1. Values returned in $formdb Value Meaning 0 In the following cases: No entities have been retrieved from a database. $formdb has been reset to 0 by a ProcScript statement. No entities are painted on the form. 1 An entity in the form has been retrieved from a database. Use Use in Form components. Description Use $formdb to test whether any occurrence in the Form has been retrieved from a database. The value of $formdb is actually the inclusive logical OR of all the entity-level flags indicating database origin. Statements that affect the value of $formdb are the same as those that affect $instancedb , and the return values are determined in the same way. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}